idas training shoes, gym footwear, stability workout shoes',NULL,'2025-11-26 09:03:07','2025-11-26 09:03:07'),(14,1,14,'Emerging Harmony Extra-Long Cover-Up | Sarinah E-Commerce','Discover the adidas Emerging Harmony Extra-Long Cover-Up, crafted with recycled and renewable materials in collaboration with KAF BY KAF. A stylish reinterpretation of traditional abayas with sporty details.','adidas cover-up, KAF BY KAF abaya, recycled polyester fashion, modest sportswear, extra-long cover-up, Sarinah E-Commerce',NULL,'2025-11-27 03:12:33','2025-11-27 03:12:33'),(15,1,15,'Ultimate365 Short Sleeve Polo Shirt | Sarinah E-Commerce','Shop the adidas Ultimate365 Short Sleeve Polo Shirt. A classic striped golf polo made with recycled polyester and elastane for comfort and sustainability.','adidas polo shirt, golf polo, Ultimate365, recycled polyester polo, sportswear, Sarinah E-Commerce',NULL,'2025-11-27 03:17:08','2025-11-27 03:17:08'),(16,1,16,'Just Do It: Nike Basketball T-Shirt | Sarinah E-Commerce','Shop the Nike Basketball T-Shirt featuring the iconic “Just Do It” slogan. Made from midweight cotton for everyday comfort and versatile style.','Nike basketball t-shirt, Just Do It tee, cotton sportswear, casual basketball shirt, Sarinah E-Commerce',NULL,'2025-11-27 03:32:23','2025-11-27 03:32:45'),(17,1,17,'Just Do It: Nike SB Skate Tee | Sarinah E-Commerce','Shop the Nike SB Skate Tee featuring the iconic “Just Do It” slogan. Made from midweight cotton for everyday comfort and versatile style.','Nike SB Skate Tee, Just Do It t-shirt, cotton skatewear, casual skate shirt, Sarinah E-Commerce',NULL,'2025-11-27 03:37:14','2025-11-27 03:37:14'),(18,1,18,'Nike Unisex Club Fleece T-Shirt in Artic Orange | Sarinah E-Commerce','Shop the Nike Unisex Club Fleece T-Shirt in Artic Orange. A casual sporty tee with soft fleece fabric, available at ASOS with extra discounts.','Nike unisex t-shirt, fleece tee, coral t-shirt, casual sportswear, ASOS exclusive, Sarinah E-Commerce',NULL,'2025-1