e','13','en','L',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-25 18:39:23','2025-11-25 18:39:23'),(144,'App\\Models\\ProductOptionValue','13','id','L',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-25 18:39:23','2025-11-25 18:39:23'),(145,'App\\Models\\ProductOptionValue','14','en','XL',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-25 18:39:23','2025-11-25 18:39:23'),(146,'App\\Models\\ProductOptionValue','14','id','XL',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-25 18:39:23','2025-11-25 18:39:23'),(147,'App\\Models\\Category','19','en','Beauty','Explore our Beauty category featuring premium skincare, makeup, and self-care essentials. Each product is carefully curated to enhance natural radiance, confidence, and everyday wellness.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:15:47','2025-11-26 03:15:47'),(148,'App\\Models\\Category','19','id','Kecantikan','Jelajahi kategori Beauty kami yang menghadirkan skincare, makeup, dan produk perawatan diri premium. Setiap produk dipilih dengan cermat untuk meningkatkan kilau alami, rasa percaya diri, dan kesehatan sehari-hari.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:15:47','2025-11-26 03:15:47'),(149,'App\\Models\\Category','20','en','Skincare','Discover our Skincare category featuring premium products for healthy, radiant skin. From cleansers and moisturizers to serums and masks, each item is carefully selected to nourish, protect, and enhance your natural glow.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:18:42','2025-11-26 03:18:42'),(150,'App\\Models\\Category','20','id','Skincare','Temukan kategori Skincare kami yang menghadirkan produk premium untuk kulit sehat dan bercahaya. Mulai dari pembersih, pelembap, hingga serum dan masker, setiap produk dipilih dengan cermat untuk menutrisi, melindungi, dan meningkatkan kilau alami kulit Anda.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:18:42','2025-11-26 03:18:42'),(151,'App\\Models\\Category','21','en','Fragrance','Indulge in our Fragrance category featuring premium perfumes and scents. From timeless classics to modern blends, each fragrance is crafted to elevate your style and leave a lasting impression.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:24:00','2025-11-26 03:24:00'),(152,'App\\Models\\Category','21','id','Fragrance','Nikmati kategori Fragrance kami yang menghadirkan parfum dan aroma premium. Dari klasik abadi hingga racikan modern, setiap wewangian dirancang untuk meningkatkan gaya Anda dan meninggalkan kesan mendalam.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:24:00','2025-11-26 03:24:00'),(153,'App\\Models\\Category','22','en','Makeup','Discover our Makeup category featuring premium cosmetics for every occasion. From foundations and lipsticks to eyeshadows and blush, each product is designed to enhance natural beauty and express personal style.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:54:00','2025-11-26 03:54:00'),(154,'App\\Models\\Category','22','id','Makeup','Temukan kategori Makeup kami yang menghadirkan kosmetik premium untuk setiap kesempatan. Mulai dari foundation dan lipstik hingga eyeshadow dan blush, setiap produk dirancang untuk menonjolkan kecantikan alami dan mengekspresikan gaya pribadi.',NULL,'2025-11-26 03:54:00','2025-11-26 03:54:00'),(155,'App\\Models\\Product','7','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The Anthony Edwards Schematic Hoodie combines athletic inspiration with modern streetwear style. Featuring bold schematic graphics and a breathable cotton blend, it\\u2019s designed for comfort and confidence both on and off the court.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"feature\":\"<ol><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Signature Anthony Edwards schematic design<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Breathable cotton-poly blend<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Athletic yet casual fit<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Durable stitching for long wear<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"material\":\"<p>70% Cotton, 30% Polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 07:36:37','2025-11-26 07:36:37'),(156,'App\\Models\\Product','7','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Anthony Edwards Schematic Hoodie memadukan inspirasi atletik dengan gaya streetwear modern. Dilengkapi grafis skematik yang berani dan bahan katun campuran yang nyaman, dirancang untuk memberikan rasa percaya diri di dalam maupun luar lapangan.<\\/p>\",\"feature\":\"<ol><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Desain skematik khas Anthony Edwards<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Bahan campuran katun-poliester yang nyaman<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Potongan atletis namun tetap kasual<\\/li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"><\\/span>Jahitan kuat untuk pemakaian jangka panjang<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"material\":\"<p>70% Katun, 30% Poliester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 07:36:37','2025-11-26 07:36:37'),(157,'App\\Models\\Product','2','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":null,\"material\":null}','2025-11-26 07:52:56','2025-11-28 02:09:21'),(158,'App\\Models\\Product','2','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":null,\"material\":null}','2025-11-26 07:52:56','2025-11-28 02:09:21'),(159,'App\\Models\\Product','8','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The Convertible Originals Hoodie Jacket is a classic golf-inspired outerwear piece with a packable hood. Designed to provide lightweight protection in changing weather, it features a timeless adidas Originals style that complements your cold-weather wardrobe.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>97% Recycled Polyamide, 3% Elastane<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:15:43','2025-11-27 07:04:16'),(160,'App\\Models\\Product','8','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Jaket Hoodie Convertible Originals adalah outerwear klasik terinspirasi golf dengan tudung yang dapat diringkas. Memberikan perlindungan ringan dalam cuaca yang berubah, dengan gaya adidas Originals yang timeless untuk melengkapi pakaian cuaca dinginmu.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>97% Poliamida Daur Ulang, 3% Elastane<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:15:43','2025-11-27 07:04:16'),(161,'App\\Models\\Product','9','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The Aeromotion Jacket is a versatile training layer designed to keep you moving in cool weather. Featuring full-zip design with hood, moisture-absorbing AEROREADY technology, and minimalist silhouette, it pairs perfectly with track pants, tights, or shorts. Made with Primegreen recycled materials for sustainable performance.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Recycled Polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:23:48','2025-11-27 07:06:50'),(162,'App\\Models\\Product','9','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":null,\"material\":null}','2025-11-26 08:23:48','2025-11-27 07:06:50'),(163,'App\\Models\\Product','10','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The Anthony Edwards Schematic Hoodie combines athletic inspiration with modern streetwear style. Featuring bold schematic graphics and a breathable cotton blend, it\\u2019s designed for comfort and confidence both on and off the court.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>70% Cotton, 30% Polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:37:28','2025-11-27 07:08:58'),(164,'App\\Models\\Product','10','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Anthony Edwards Schematic Hoodie memadukan inspirasi atletik dengan gaya streetwear modern. Dilengkapi grafis skematik yang berani dan bahan katun campuran yang nyaman, dirancang untuk memberikan rasa percaya diri di dalam maupun luar lapangan.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>70% Katun, 30% Poliester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:37:28','2025-11-27 07:08:58'),(165,'App\\Models\\Product','11','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The adidas by Stella McCartney Peplum Hoodie blends sporty DNA with feminine elegance. Featuring a loose fit and adjustable peplum hem, it offers versatile styling for running, training, or casual outings. Crafted with organic cotton and recycled polyester for sustainable comfort.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>60% Organic Cotton, 40% Recycled Polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:46:50','2025-11-27 07:10:27'),(166,'App\\Models\\Product','11','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Hoodie Peplum adidas by Stella McCartney memadukan DNA sporty dengan sentuhan feminin elegan. Dengan potongan longgar dan keliman peplum yang dapat disesuaikan, hoodie ini serbaguna untuk lari, latihan, maupun gaya santai. Dibuat dari katun organik dan poliester daur ulang untuk kenyamanan berkelanjutan.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>60% Katun Organik, 40% Poliester Daur Ulang<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:46:50','2025-11-27 07:10:27'),(167,'App\\Models\\Product','12','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The Terrex Graphic Tee is crafted for outdoor enthusiasts who value comfort and style. Made with soft single jersey cotton, it offers a breathable fit for all-day wear. The bold back graphic highlights adidas\\u2019 dedication to outdoor adventure.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Cotton (Better Cotton initiative)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:53:42','2025-11-27 07:13:40'),(168,'App\\Models\\Product','12','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Terrex Graphic Tee dibuat untuk pencinta outdoor yang mengutamakan kenyamanan dan gaya. Terbuat dari katun single jersey yang lembut, memberikan kenyamanan bernapas untuk dipakai seharian. Graphic berani di bagian belakang menegaskan dedikasi adidas pada petualangan outdoor.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Katun (Better Cotton initiative)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 08:53:42','2025-11-27 07:13:40'),(169,'App\\Models\\Product','13','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>The adidas Dropset 2 Trainer is built for strength training and stability. With a low midsole drop and wide base, it provides a solid foundation for squats, deadlifts, and high-intensity workouts. Breathable mesh upper and durable rubber outsole ensure comfort and grip during every session.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p> Textile upper, Rubber outsole<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 09:03:07','2025-11-27 07:15:31'),(170,'App\\Models\\Product','13','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>adidas Dropset 2 Trainer dirancang untuk latihan kekuatan dan stabilitas. Dengan midsole drop rendah dan alas yang lebar, sepatu ini memberikan fondasi kokoh untuk squat, deadlift, dan latihan intensitas tinggi. Upper mesh yang bernapas dan outsole karet yang tahan lama memastikan kenyamanan serta grip di setiap sesi.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>Upper tekstil, Outsole karet<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-26 09:03:07','2025-11-27 07:15:31'),(171,'App\\Models\\Product','14','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>A modern reinterpretation of traditional abayas, this adidas extra-long cover-up blends soft recycled polyester with renewable materials. Designed in collaboration with Saudi luxury fashion label KAF BY KAF, it features a relaxed fit, open front, and sporty rubber-print 3-Stripes for versatile layering.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% recycled polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:12:33','2025-11-27 07:17:27'),(172,'App\\Models\\Product','14','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Sebuah reinterpretasi modern dari abaya tradisional, cover-up ekstra panjang adidas ini memadukan poliester daur ulang dengan material terbarukan. Dirancang bersama label mewah asal Saudi, KAF BY KAF, tampil dengan potongan longgar, bagian depan terbuka, serta detail sporty 3-Stripes untuk gaya berlapis yang serbaguna.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% recycled polyester<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:12:33','2025-11-27 07:17:27'),(173,'App\\Models\\Product','15','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Classic plays well everywhere. This adidas golf polo pairs stripe details with a regular cut and stretch jersey for distraction-free rounds. Made with recycled polyester and elastane, it offers comfort and sustainability for every game.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>89% polyester (recycled), 11% elastane \\u2013 single jersey<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:17:07','2025-11-27 07:19:05'),(174,'App\\Models\\Product','15','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Klasik cocok di mana saja. Polo golf adidas ini memadukan detail garis dengan potongan reguler dan bahan jersey elastis untuk permainan tanpa gangguan. Terbuat dari poliester daur ulang dan elastane, memberikan kenyamanan sekaligus keberlanjutan di setiap permainan.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>89% polyester (recycled), 11% elastane \\u2013 single jersey<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:17:07','2025-11-27 07:19:05'),(175,'App\\Models\\Product','16','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>You don\\u2019t win first by thinking twice. This Nike Basketball T-Shirt is crafted from midweight cotton for everyday comfort. Featuring the iconic \\u201cJust Do It\\u201d slogan, it\\u2019s a sure thing for versatile styling both on and off the court.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Cotton (midweight)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:32:23','2025-11-27 07:21:04'),(176,'App\\Models\\Product','16','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Kamu tidak akan jadi juara dengan ragu-ragu. T-Shirt Nike Basketball ini dibuat dari katun midweight untuk kenyamanan sehari-hari. Dengan slogan ikonik \\u201cJust Do It\\u201d, kaos ini pasti cocok untuk gaya serbaguna di dalam maupun luar lapangan.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Cotton (midweight)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:32:23','2025-11-27 07:21:04'),(177,'App\\Models\\Product','17','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>You don\\u2019t win first by thinking twice. This Nike SB Skate Tee is crafted from midweight cotton for everyday comfort. Featuring the iconic \\u201cJust Do It\\u201d slogan, it\\u2019s a sure thing for versatile styling both on and off the board.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Cotton (midweight)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:37:14','2025-11-27 07:27:10'),(178,'App\\Models\\Product','17','id',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>Kamu tidak akan jadi juara dengan ragu-ragu. T-Shirt Nike SB Skate ini dibuat dari katun midweight untuk kenyamanan sehari-hari. Dengan slogan ikonik \\u201cJust Do It\\u201d, kaos ini pasti cocok untuk gaya serbaguna di atas maupun di luar papan skate.<\\/p>\",\"material\":\"<p>100% Cotton (midweight)<\\/p>\"}','2025-11-27 03:37:14','2025-11-27 07:27:10'),(179,'App\\Models\\Product','18','en',NULL,NULL,'{\"story\":\"<p>A ver